videoSnippet.title: The agadmator Podcast #2 || Hikaru Nakamura
videoSnippet.description:
Check out my game against Hikaru here https://youtu.be/TgPp7ltPd8Y

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL5YbN5WLFD8dLIegT5QAbA/join

Hello everyone!
This is the second podcast and I hope you will enjoy. The guest is none other than Hikaru Nakamura.
We discuss online chess, Classical, Pogchamps, future of chess, chess in general, Hikaru's personal life and finish the episode off with some questions from my subscribers.

At the end of the session, we play a chess game (5min blitz game), you can check my analysis of the game here (link will be available when the podcast airs)

Listen to the audio version here (link available soon)
Podcast is also available on Spotify and will soon be on Google Podcasts and Apple Podcasts.
